My top 9 of 2019. Thank you so much to everyone who has shown your appreciation and support for my work, gotten tattoos from me, and been there when I needed encouragement.

An even bigger thank you to my beautiful wife, to my friends and to everyone who helped make @thirdeyequito a reality. I’m so lucky to have the opportunity to open my own studio, and even more so to have a team as creatively talented and amazing as @mishell.estevez and @micaela_koenig. You’re both incredible.

Here’s to 2019, a year of changes and challenges and triumphs. Now let’s see what 2020 and the next decade will bring!
